{"tid":1095324,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"處女拍劇男友完全無教戲 張寶兒：他讓我自由發揮","createTime":"2019-04-07T03:05:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-08T04:07:05.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f74a36226272e7abbec73789eb7a9bd0e7b0cf09","tid":1095324,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T03:05:48.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】《鐵探》部分主要演員前晚約齊飯局睇劇，席間張寶兒提到首次拍劇，男友袁偉豪卻沒有指導她演戲。在旁的王君馨聽到其言後，不禁大讚她第一次拍劇已表現得很好，還笑言自己首次拍劇時只懂望地下。<br />\n無 劇集《鐵探》部分主要演員，包括袁偉豪、許紹雄、梁競徽、張寶兒及王君馨等等，前晚出席飯局睇劇兼宣傳。問到收視或內地視頻網可有好消息，袁偉豪表示香港收視仍未有確實數字，但內地網站總評《鐵探》有7.8分，他說：「相信反應會愈來愈好，劇情開始緊張。昨晚跟屋企人睇洪永城死那一幕，屋企人都擰轉面不敢看，反應好好。」問到此劇是否其代表作？袁偉豪說：「都算係。（拍得咁辛苦都抵？）多謝大家賞識，都希望工作上尋求突破。」<br />\n<br />\n君馨不介意包尾生B<br />\n此外，張寶兒首次拍劇，她透露父母都會跟她一同收看。她特別感謝劇組全體人員的包容及教導，因拍攝時才發現拍劇跟綜藝有很大分別。問到男友袁偉豪可有教演戲？她笑笑說：「他沒理我，畀我自由發揮。」身旁的王君馨大讚她第一次拍劇表現已經很好，還記得自己第一次拍劇，唸對白時只懂望地下。<br />\n另外，談到日前她好姊妹鍾嘉欣、苟芸慧、岑麗香、李亞男聚會。她表示非常愉快，整晚都以湊小朋友為話題。笑指她未能參與此話題，君馨笑說：「可以學住先。（預 包尾？）我想 ，我有叫苟姑娘加油，我守龍門都無所謂。」她幻想她們五姊妹再加十個小朋友拍節目會非常有趣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/86gIzCLo5iLisuqLQ4CsAQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MDtpbD1wbGFuZQ--/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/D04a_enp03p01070419copy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F86gIzCLo5iLisuqLQ4CsAQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MDtpbD1wbGFuZQ--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2FD04a_enp03p01070419copy.jpg&h=189a5bc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/fdUC.tZkJupy_kuYMiyZjw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MDtpbD1wbGFuZQ--/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/D04a_enp03p02070419copy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FfdUC.tZkJupy_kuYMiyZjw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MDtpbD1wbGFuZQ--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2FD04a_enp03p02070419copy.jpg&h=c4f12659&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/sYAp5lIriX2ZgAyZeTrLZg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MDtpbD1wbGFuZQ--/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/D04a_enp03p03070419copy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FsYAp5lIriX2ZgAyZeTrLZg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MDtpbD1wbGFuZQ--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2FD04a_enp03p03070419copy.jpg&h=b2ab30eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/eumSPdzyscGTxdqEHUMSaQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MDtpbD1wbGFuZQ--/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/D04a_enp03p04070419copy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FeumSPdzyscGTxdqEHUMSaQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MDtpbD1wbGFuZQ--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2FD04a_enp03p04070419copy.jpg&h=f62febf1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%99%95%E5%A5%B3%E6%8B%8D%E5%8A%87%E7%94%B7%E5%8F%8B%E5%AE%8C%E5%85%A8%E7%84%A1%E6%95%99%E6%88%B2-%E5%BC%B5%E5%AF%B6%E5%85%92-%E4%BB%96%E8%AE%93%E6%88%91%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E7%99%BC%E6%8F%AE-220428481.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E8%2599%2595%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E6%258B%258D%25E5%258A%2587%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%258F%258B%25E5%25AE%258C%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%2595%2599%25E6%2588%25B2-%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E5%25AF%25B6%25E5%2585%2592-%25E4%25BB%2596%25E8%25AE%2593%25E6%2588%2591%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2594%25B1%25E7%2599%25BC%25E6%258F%25AE-220428481.html&d=bZmkWp0iUYBi2b5pBzw%2FEf%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=f13baa5d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%99%95%E5%A5%B3%E6%8B%8D%E5%8A%87%E7%94%B7%E5%8F%8B%E5%AE%8C%E5%85%A8%E7%84%A1%E6%95%99%E6%88%B2-%E5%BC%B5%E5%AF%B6%E5%85%92-%E4%BB%96%E8%AE%93%E6%88%91%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E7%99%BC%E6%8